Map -silent [n] <Space>l <C-w>l
Map -silent [n] <Space>n <C-w>w
Map -silent [n] <Space>p <C-w>W

Map -silent [n] <Space><Space>j <C-w>J
Map -silent [n] <Space><Space>k <C-w>K
